OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLate sunny
OL,6,Fspells as showers clear away this
OL,7,Fevening. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fsee mostly dry conditions, perhaps the
OL,9,Fodd light shower in the west. Patchy
OL,10,Frural frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FFairly cloudy but dry for most
OL,13,Fplaces. The best of the sunnier spells
OL,14,Fare expected early in the morning and
OL,15,Flate in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
